    "body": "Extracts `DataDirTestingSetup` from `BasicTestingSetup`. The latter no longer creates a datadir nor logs to a file by default.\r\n\r\nImproves run-times of quicker tests (4 warmups + 60 runs each):\r\n| Command | Mean [ms] | Relative |\r\n|:---|---:|---:|\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t addrman_tests (commit = 2fe76ed8)`    | 246.6 ± 2.3   | 1.13 ± 0.01 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t addrman_tests (commit = 1a0ce432)`    | 218.3 ± 0.7   | 1.00 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t checkqueue_tests (commit = 2fe76ed8)` | 1.273 ± 0.062 | 1.23 ± 0.15 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t checkqueue_tests (commit = 1a0ce432)` | 1.034 ± 0.118 | 1.00 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t merkle_tests (commit = 2fe76ed8)`     | 698.6 ± 4.3   | 1.15 ± 0.01 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t merkle_tests (commit = 1a0ce432)`     | 606.4 ± 2.3   | 1.00 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t orphanage_tests (commit = 2fe76ed8)`  | 233.9 ± 11.9  | 1.41 ± 0.07 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t orphanage_tests (commit = 1a0ce432)`  | 165.5 ± 0.3   | 1.00 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t util_tests (commit = 2fe76ed8)`       | 148.7 ± 1.7   | 1.12 ± 0.02 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t util_tests (commit = 1a0ce432)`       | 132.3 ± 1.1   | 1.00 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t validation_tests (commit = 2fe76ed8)` | 197.2 ± 1.9   | 1.63 ± 0.02 |\r\n| `test_bitcoin -t validation_tests (commit = 1a0ce432)` | 121.1 ± 0.2   | 1.00 |\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nRemoved overhead is barely measurable on test suite runtime.\r\n\r\nRelative speed comparison (1 warmup + 5 runs each), sequential execution\r\n        1.01 ±  0.00  `test_bitcoin` (commit = 2fe76ed8)\r\n        1.00          `test_bitcoin` (commit = 1a0ce432)\r\n\r\nRelative speed comparison (1 warmup + 5 runs each), parallel execution (+ more tests)\r\n        1.00 ±  0.01  `ctest --test-dir build` (commit = 2fe76ed8)\r\n        1.00          `ctest --test-dir build` (commit = 1a0ce432)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nFollow-up to https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/34562#discussion_r2918752158\r\nArguably in a similar vein as #22086.",
