      "message": "test+fuzz+bench: Extract DataDirTestingSetup from BasicTestingSetup\n\nMany tests don't need files on disk, so creating a datadir for BasicTestingSetup and logging to disk is no longer done by default.\n\nThe MakeNoLogFileContext<BasicTestingSetup> combination still serves a purpose in disabling debug logging though.\n\nIn a similar vein as https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22086 \"test: remove BasicTestingSetup from unit tests that don't need it\"",
